{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.inova.twskit\/documentation\/TWSKit"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"sections":[],"kind":"article","metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"TWSKit"}],"title":"Handling Google Login","role":"article","roleHeading":"Article"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/com.inova.twskit\/documentation\/TWSKit\/GoogleLogin"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A quick guide to handling Google Login in your snippets"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"text":"Overview","type":"heading","anchor":"overview","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Google has implemented security around their login functionality. As such, you are unable to successfully complete the login process within the snippet. This means that in order to get the functionality to work, you’ll need to handle the login in your phone’s browser and then handle the response.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This guide will show you how","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"text":"Setup universal links","type":"heading","anchor":"Setup-universal-links"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You’ll need to setup UniversalLinks for your app on the domain you’re trying to login with Google. Make sure you check the URL that GoogleLogin calls after the login. You need to match the URL in your paths. In this sample the path “"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\/__\/auth\/handler"},{"text":"” is used. The same path also needs to be provided, if you’re building the project with CLI. More info about that can be found in the dedicated CLI link, found on the main page.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Your assetlinks.json should look like this:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":null,"code":["{","    \"applinks\": {","        \"details\": [","            {","                \"appID\": <Insert your bundle ID>,","                \"paths\": [","                    \"\/__\/auth\/handler\"","                ]","            }","        ]","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You can read more about UniversalLinks in Apple’s documentation: ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/xcode\/supporting-associated-domains"}]},{"text":"Handle incoming URL","anchor":"Handle-incoming-URL","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.inova.twskit\/documentation\/TWSKit\/TWSView"},{"type":"text","text":" you’re using will now automatically handle the redirects from the phone’s browser."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/twskit\/googlelogin"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://com.inova.twskit/documentation/TWSKit":{"type":"topic","title":"TWSKit","url":"\/documentation\/twskit","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.inova.twskit\/documentation\/TWSKit","role":"collection","abstract":[{"text":"SDK for creating custom mobile apps","type":"text"}]},"doc://com.inova.twskit/documentation/TWSKit/TWSView":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The main view to use to display snippets"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"TWSView","url":"\/documentation\/twskit\/twsview","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"TWSView"}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.inova.twskit\/documentation\/TWSKit\/TWSView","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"TWSView"}]},"https://developer.apple.com/documentation/xcode/supporting-associated-domains":{"type":"link","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/xcode\/supporting-associated-domains","title":"Universal Links","url":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/xcode\/supporting-associated-domains","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"Universal Link